text: Revenge of the Flame () is a 1956 Turkish drama film directed by Osman F. Seden. It stars Ayhan Isik, Mualla Kaynak, Kenan Pars, Deniz Tanyeli, Turgut Özatay, Nubar Terziyan and Temel Karamahmut. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1956 films Category:Turkish films Category:Turkish drama films Category:1956 drama films
